title: >>> FEAST WEEK
body_text:
Short and sweet ... The Thanksgiving Special ...
Dodgeball enters into its unbelievable 65th event, headlined by another [apparent] challenge from Pond Scum. It was rumored last week that members of the rival stable would show up. That did not happen however and the night took on a classic role (with exception to light problem).
Will Pond Scum avenge their loss from LX3? With they have a bigger army this time?
With the new
Fantasy Warfare
section, will any "dream matches" be witnessed?
This is yet another significant event in dodgeball history. Do not miss out!
